01:09:26,078 --> 01:09:27,163
Apa kata laluannya?

772
01:09:27,246 --> 01:09:29,790
- Hari lahir awak.
- Kenapa guna hari lahir saya?

773
01:09:29,874 --> 01:09:31,709
