778
01:11:29,785 --> 01:11:31,870
{\an8}Siapa awak? Hantu?

779
01:11:31,954 --> 01:11:33,956
{\an8}Tolong lepaskan saya, kali ini saja.

780
01:11:36,333 --> 01:11:37,459
{\an8}Itu Biro Kawalan.

