787
01:11:48,137 --> 01:11:49,305
{\an8}Saya takkan mati hari ini.

788
01:11:49,388 --> 01:11:50,514
{\an8}<i>Awak membawanya?</i>

789
01:11:51,098 --> 01:11:52,891
