791
01:11:55,894 --> 01:11:57,021
{\an8}<i>Apa yang penting</i>

792
01:11:57,104 --> 01:11:58,897
{\an8}<i>bukanlah tempatnya.</i>

793
01:11:59,481 --> 01:12:01,483
{\an8}- Siapa mereka?
