794
01:12:02,234 --> 01:12:03,944
{\an8}<i>Mereka memang kejam.</i>

795
01:12:04,028 --> 01:12:07,823
{\an8}<i>Sekali ditangkap,
mereka takkan lepaskan awak.</i>

796
01:12:08,324 --> 01:12:11,827
{\an8}Kalau awak nak tahu apa berlaku,
dengar cakap saya.

797
